overview: Join hosts Hannah Rad and Rani KoHEnur for the 2nd annual “House of Pride” brought to you by McDonald’s! This year’s show kicks off pride season in style with celebratory musical performances by Keiynan Lonsdale, Frankie Simone, Rani KoHEnur, and the House of Ebony. Also featuring special comedy sets by Kia Barnes and Sampson McCormick–and a showstopping opening number with superstars Mila Jam, Madison Rose, and Julian King–you won’t want to miss a visit to this “House!”
title: House of Pride 2022
